config BR2_PACKAGE_BMT_NPU_STUB
	bool "bmt-npu-stub (hardware acceleration placeholder)"
	depends on BR2_aarch64
	help
	  Placeholder package for NPU/GPU hardware acceleration.

	  At runtime the controller auto-detects the available accelerator
	  and loads the appropriate backend:

	    Jetson Orin Nano Super  — CUDA / TensorRT (NVIDIA JetPack BSP)
	    RK3588                  — RKNN runtime / RKLLM
	    Pi 5 + Hailo AI HAT+ 2  — HailoRT
	    QEMU / Apple Silicon    — CPU-only fallback (llama.cpp)

	  Replace this stub with the real BSP package recipe for each target.
	  Do NOT enable CUDA, RKNN, or HailoRT on QEMU targets.
